---
title: Tropical Beef Bowls with Mango Salsa
description: Forget the 14-hour flight and flower lei – we’re packing all the deliciousness of a luau feast into one quick and delicious dish! You’re about to experience a melange of sweet and savoury flavours inspired by the Aloha state. A bright mango and tomato salsa, creamy garlic-lime crema, lightly charred veggies and crispy teriyaki beef are all arranged over fluffy basmati ice. Prepare your taste buds for a trip to the tropics.
